original_title: A Casa do Mickey Mouse: Rodeio dos Números
overview: Rustle up some fun! Howdy Mousekeroos! It's time to put on your cowboy hats, grab your lassos and help Mickey, Goofy, and all your Clubhouse pals wrangle a boisterous herd of wild numbers into Mickey Corral. Laugh it up as you count 'em down from 10 to 1, and rustle up the right Mouseketools to catch those rascally numbers! Then search for Daisy Bo Peep's lost sheep, decode a secret message, and solve more super fun puzzles. For big surprises and rootin', tootin' fun from sun up to sundown, count on Mickey's Numbers Round-Up!
title: Mickey Mouse Clubhouse: Numbers Roundup
